Create Embedded CSS Styles between "head" tags of your template.

== Description ==

This plugin will allow wordpress developers, site administrators, theme designers to create embedded css style sheet within "head" tag of any wordpress theme with own class,id names.

Author's Website : http://www.mclanka.com


== Installation ==

1. Unzip the embedded-style-sheet-plugin-for-wordpress.zip file.
2. Upload the `embedded-style-sheet-plugin-for-wordpress` folder to the `/wp-content/plugins/` directory.
3. Activate the plugin through the 'Plugins' menu in WordPress.
4. Go to Settings =>  Ustyle

